{"type": "article", "id": 13582, "title": "电动冲浪滑板", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-17T07:55:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105804EIy9ncDlPSoWHJi3.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t很多人喜欢冲浪，但有时间条件限制，所在的地区可能没有成片的海水，而河水又难以满足他们肾上腺素飙升的感觉。于是，Onean 推出的这款电动冲浪滑板就是为他们体贴考虑后设计的，滑板采用电力，有足够的马力满足在河里冲浪的需求，同时，还有不同的马力可以选择。<a href=\"http://www.onean.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141324aXm7H6SAFBCQTWUI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55745721\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141325T3K0jH4DOb5zeqCc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141325r7C4vegMT8yQuOZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413265XUW7xNtf8Mbm6VS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413267tv9VYHuXWJyAdhR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141327kMDG9b6fehKc7Zop.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54523227\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}